		<div class="box_shadow">
			<div class="eightcol main_col">
				<div class="h1_spacer"><h1 style="width: 350px;"><strong>Learning Resource Centre</strong></h1></div>
<p>Alberta Bible College's Learning Resource Centre exists to provide the students and faculty of Alberta Bible College with the necessary resources to support the curriculum offered by the college.</p>

<div style="float: left; width: 45%; margin-right: 5%;">
	<h3>Online Catalog</h3>

	<form class="text_center" name="searchform" target="_blank" method="get" action="http://abccatalog.kohacatalog.com/cgi-bin/koha/opac-search.pl" style="background-color: #56809e; border: solid thin #263956; padding:10px 5px 10px 5px;">
		<input type="text" style="background-color: #f3f3f3;" name="q">
		<input type="submit" value="Search Catalog">
	</form>

	<p><strong>Search and view articles</strong> in periodical databases:</p>
	<ul type="circle">
		<li><a href="http://search.ebscohost.com/">Search online periodical databases (ATLAS)</a></li>
		<li><a href="http://routledgeonline.com/religion/">Online reference works (Routledge Religion)</a></li>
	</ul>
	<p><a href="http://www.ccli.com/">Find lyric and chord charts (Song Select)</a></p>
	<p><a href="http://www.talonline.ca/">Access other libraries (The Alberta Library Catalogue)</a></p>
	<p><a href="/writingguidelines">Access help with writing assignments</a></p>
</div>

<div style="float: left; width: 50%;">
	<h3>Hours of Operation</h3>
		<div style="margin-top: 1.8em;"><strong>Regular Hours</strong></div>
		<ul style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">
			<li>Monday to Thursday – 9am to 9pm</li>
			<li>Friday – 9am to 5pm</li>
			<li>Saturdays – 10am to 2pm</li>
			<li>Closed Sundays, Long Weekends &amp; Statutory Holidays</li>
		</ul>
	<div style="margin-top: 1.8em;"><strong>Summer Hours</strong></div>
		<ul style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">
			<li>Monday to Friday – 9am to 12pm &amp; 1pm to 4pm</li>
			<li>Saturday &amp; Sunday – Closed</li>
			<li>Closed Statutory Holidays</li>
		</ul>
		<div>Summer hours start after graduation and end after the first full week of classes in September. Please call before your visit if you are unsure.</div>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>

<h3>Onsite resources</h3>
<ul>
	<li>
		<h5 class="black">Books and Periodicals</h5>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">Over 30,000 print and electronic resources onsite, with access to over 140,000 resources through the Southern Alberta Libraries of Theology Consortium.</div>
	</li>
	<li>
		<h5 class="black">Ministry Resources</h5>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">For practical ministry with children, youth, drama or music.</div>
	</li>
	<li>
		<h5 class="black">Workspaces, Desktop Computers and Wireless Network</h5>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">Available for library patrons</div>
	</li>
	<li>
		<h5 class="black">Reading Nooks</h5>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">Many comfortable places to sit and read</div>
	</li>
	<li>
		<h5 class="black">Photocopier and Printer</h5>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">The printer is behind the Learning Resource Centre desk and only Learning Resource Centre staff have access to this printer. Please ask for printing. The fee is $0.10 for black and white printing. Colour printing is available by request for $0.25 per sheet. Fees still apply in cases of mistaken printing. Pre-paid cards may be purchased from Learning Resource Centre staff or the Business Office. No credit will be given.
		</div>
	</li>
	<li>
		<h5 class="black">Alumni Borrowing Privileges</h5>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">ABC alumni may make use of the Alberta Bible College Learning Resource Centre including borrowing privileges. This service is free of charge, but basic contact information is required in order to contact you if necessary.</div>
	</li>
	<li>
		<h5 class="black">Community User Card</h5>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">As of August 1, 2015, members of the Christian or local community may make use of the Alberta Bible College Learning Resource Centre, including borrowing privileges, for an annual fee of $25.00.  Basic contact information is required in order to contact you if necessary.</div>
	</li>
	<li>
		<h5 class="black">Exam Invigilation Services</h5>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">Regional exam centre for the University of South Africa &amp; Queen’s University, Ontario.</div>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">Independent exam invigilation: $25.00/exam</div>
		<div style="margin-left:1em;">Please email <a href="&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#058;library@abccampus.ca" target="_blank">library@abccampus.ca</a> for more information</div>
	</li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any questions regarding our Learning Resource Centre, call 403-282-2994 ext. 234 or email <a href="&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#058;library@abccampus.ca" target="_blank">library@abccampus.ca</a></p>			</div>
